name: Drank After Work #05 // Drunk Vegans
description: My old friend W. was a designer who always wore expensive sunglasses. He got wasted and partied every night. The next morning he would always say, "Fuck, I'm going to be vegan" and eat like 3 avocados. Then 5 hours later, he forgot about being a vegan and started to drink again. Drank life!
